The paper deals with the task of sketch-based image retrieval, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed approach involves deep learning models, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses evaluation metrics and benchmark datasets, which are relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
